snippet.title: Super Mario Bros. Crossover 3.0 Trailer
snippet.description:
This is the trailer for version 3.0 of Super Mario Bros. Crossover. For more info, see http://www.explodingrabbit.com/videos/super-mario-crossover-3-0-trailer

Today is also the three year anniversary of the game, so happy anniversary!
